      "title": "INSTRUCTIONS",
      "content": "<p class=\"c10\"><span class=\"c4\"></span></p><ul class=\"c2 lst-kix_nap7staus29z-0 start\" data-indent=\"0\"><li class=\"c13 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c4\">Copy the article Title xxx reports bit below and paste it somewhere to make a new article</span></li><li class=\"c13 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c4\">Write your article</span></li></ul><ul class=\"c2 lst-kix_nap7staus29z-1 start\" data-indent=\"1\"><li class=\"c18 c20 c19 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c4\">Use headings from h2 to h5</span></li></ul><ul class=\"c2 lst-kix_nap7staus29z-2 start\" data-indent=\"2\"><li class=\"c9 li-bullet-0\"><span style=\"overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 346.00px; height: 719.00px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXcGRS9h-Gb1i16ZV7CAIGB7soElzGiFVKBgOzJEdBbtf8-7VHvBMtrNaDs63veMK5Rd5AhHJjHOtk6tjcyP96HAl0hBwlijDs2T9qOtYzamrhA-K2PqXYE9qPJQuWbcaA?key=254Go52j4RkdLoOv2J36DQ\" style=\"width: 346.00px; height: 719.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);\" title=\"\"></span></li></ul><ul class=\"c2 lst-kix_nap7staus29z-1\" data-indent=\"1\"><li class=\"c18 c20 c19 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c4\">Use heading 6 to caption images</span></li><li class=\"c18 c19 c20 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c4\">Make images full width and set to “break text”</span></li></ul><ul class=\"c2 lst-kix_nap7staus29z-2 start\" data-indent=\"2\"><li class=\"c9 li-bullet-0\"><span style=\"overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 366.00px; height: 159.00px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXeXObSZ3bd0a74l2Lceysc