    {
      "title": "Dodd Fell TDA",
      "content": "<h5 class=\"c5\" id=\"h.jggahqad0m9h\"><span class=\"c0\">Simon Hulme reports</span></h5><p class=\"c10\"><span class=\"c4\"></span></p><p class=\"c18\"><span>As reported in </span><span class=\"c6\" style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><a class=\"c8\" href=\"https://www.dhpc.org.uk/skywords/#url=https://docs.google.com/document/d/e/2PACX-1vSv7aTai2yfObOHeDmYhtKpXFTQejk7imMRBqzlefdnvKGEHtBsWLlF-xIGUSbMphLnwFub-9jrvHaR/pub\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">last month’s SkyWords</a></span><span class=\"c4\">, there's an Airspace Change Proposal in progress with the CAA to fly a Beyond Visual Line Of Sight (BVLOS) drone at Dodd Fell this summer which covers the key part of the Dodd ridge line and the majority of the valley below.</span></p><p class=\"c10\"><span class=\"c4\"></span></p><p class=\"c18\"><span class=\"c4\">The only update since last month is that the club has submitted our official response.</span></p><p class=\"c10\"><span class=\"c4\"></span></p><p class=\"c18\"><span class=\"c4\">&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; SUMMARY OF RESPONSE &lt;&lt;&lt; &nbsp;with link to full version in forum</span></p><p class=\"c10\"><span class=\"c4\"></span></p><p class=\"c18\"><span style=\"overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 786.14px; height: 624.00px;\"><img alt=\"Position of proposed TDA overlaid on the Dodd/Wether area tracklogs.\" src=\"https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXd7CFHdBlsTE75--aNi5ifuOOtPdz4WwtZFJdDkG2rzU5PG5SOaJmQBTYSB5bDIFnWrDpIT-r4pwqZff-Jh0mZVfayZF2fDOXrMBVQJ0oqAFhJ8tCZfiiLysWhBeUotDtk?key=254Go52j4RkdLoOv2J36DQ\" style=\"width: 786.14px; height: 624.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);\" title=\"\"></span></p><h6 class=\"c21\" id=\"h.oenmzoglsq7b\"><span>Area of the TDA overlaid on the PG soaring heatmap from</span><span><a class=\"c8\" href=\"https://www.dhpc.org.uk/forum/thermal.kk7.ch\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">&nbsp;</a></span><span class=\"c6\" style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><a class=\"c8\" href=\"https://www.dhpc.org.uk/forum/thermal.kk7.ch\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">thermal.kk7.ch</a></span><span class=\"c16\" style=\"font-style:italic\">&nbsp;(approximate) </span></h6><p class=\"c10\"><span class=\"c4\"></span></p>",
